# {{.Name}} ({{.Type}})

Manages an ISHosting VPS instance.

~> **Important:** ISHosting does not support deleting VPS instances via the API. When you run `terraform destroy`, the provider will **disable auto-renew** on the instance instead. The VPS will remain active until the end of the current billing period and will not be renewed after that.

